title: Hellboy Universe, Complete as of December 2013
description:
This includes:

- Hellboy
- Hellboy in Hell
- B.P.R.D
- B.P.R.D: Hell on Earth
- Lobster Johnson
- Abe Sapien
- Sir Edward Grey, Witchfinder
- Sledgehammer 44


This is an update on my older torrent. I went after whatever was missing from it. Far as I know there is no Hellboy collection online more up to date than this one. 

As always, if you like the comics, find a way to support the author! Buy the hardcover collection of your favorite arc, or something.


For more awesome indie comics, feel free to check my profile. Let me know if there is anything you're looking for - I might have it.
